title: Week 12 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Injury Tilt! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/29
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 12! Which performances are the most surprising and the most worrisome for the rest of the fantasy football season? Plus, lots of injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 29th, 2021.
  
 (04:10) - Monday Punday
 (10:10) - NFL News 
 (21:40) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (22:20) - QB Studs
 (24:10) - RB Studs
 (33:15) - WR Studs
 (38:15) - TE Studs
 (40:20) - Fantasy Duds
 (40:25) - QB Duds
 (43:45) - RB Duds
 (47:35) - WR Duds
 (50:35) - TE Duds
